      "description_mirror": {
        "type": "doc",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Join the Stripe founder community for a day of hands-on building and coworking with the Stripe team. Whether you’re looking for a chance to connect with other founders, 1:1 guidance from the Stripe team, or just a change of scenery, we’d love to have you join.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Build Days are coworking days with Stripe, designed specifically for founders—whether you’re already building on Stripe or just getting started. Plus, get lunch, coffee, and swag on us. ",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Don’t miss the morning as we kick off with an intimate fireside chat featuring Zach Lloyd, CEO of ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "text": "Warp.dev",
                "type": "text",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "link",
                    "attrs": {
                      "href": "https://Warp.dev"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": ". Warp is an agentic development environment that empowers developers to ship better software more quickly. Previously a principal engineer at Google, cofounder and CTO at SelfMade, and interim CTO at TIME, Zach will walk us through the founding journey of Warp. Join us in the room to hear his practical advice on how to build and scale a company in the AI era.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "You’ll also get to see demos of Stripe’s latest products directly from the product teams, so you can leave with insights on how to monetize your AI product, build multisided marketplaces, scale in global markets, and more.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Don't miss out on",
                "type": "text",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "bold"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bullet_list",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "An intimate fireside chat with Zach Lloyd, CEO of Warp",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "Hands-on integration support from Stripe experts",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
